    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not-assessed at Gradation 1 per MRL 2 requirements. GCI < 5% for primary QoIs. RH index validated within experimental uncertainty across all configurations. UQ campaign results reviewed by the team confirm that inlet flow rate is the dominant uncertainty driver and that worst-case identification is robust to ±10% input perturbations. The CFD model is assessed as sufficiently credible to support the COU decision for the Class II CPB device. Decision: Accepted.",
